    "page-proj-incidents":  "\u003cdiv class=\"page\" id=\"page-proj-incidents\"\u003e\n      \u003cdiv class=\"card\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;border-color:var(--danger)\"\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"card-header\" style=\"background:#FEF3F2;border-radius:11px 11px 0 0\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"badge badge-red\"\u003e🔴 严重\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan style=\"font-weight:600\"\u003e支付服务 NullPointerException - mall-backend\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cspan class=\"badge badge-yellow\"\u003e处理中\u003c/span\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003cdiv class=\"card-body\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"grid-2\"\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \u003cdiv style=\"font-weight:600;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:8px\"\u003e错误堆栈\u003c/div\u003e\n              \u003cdiv class=\"code-block\" style=\"font-size:11px;height:100px;overflow:auto\"\u003ejava.lang.NullPointerException\u003cbr\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;at PaymentService.processOrder(:142)\u003cbr\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cm\"\u003eCaused by: order.paymentMethod is null\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \u003cdiv class=\"ai-label\"\u003e🤖 AI 诊断\u003c/div\u003e\n              \u003cdiv class=\"ai-bubble\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e根因：\u003c/strong\u003echeckout 接口未对 paymentMethod 做非空校验。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e修复：\u003c/strong\u003e?OrderController:89 加参数校验。\u003cbr\u003e\u003cbutton class=\"btn btn-primary\" style=\"font-size:12px;padding:4px 10px;margin-top:8px\"\u003e🤖 ?IDE 中修复\u003c/button\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e",
